dataset_id: CMS: Mangrove Canopy Height Estimates from Remote Imagery, Zambezi Delta, Mozambique
title: CMS: Mangrove Canopy Height Estimates from Remote Imagery, Zambezi Delta, Mozambique
summary: This data set provides high resolution canopy height estimates for mangrove forests in the Zambezi Delta, Mozambique, Africa. The estimates were derived from three separate canopy height models (CHM) using airborne Lidar data, stereophotogrammetry with WorldView 1 imagery, and Interferometric-Synthetic Aperture Radar (In-SAR) techniques with TanDEM-X imagery. The data cover the period 2011-10-14 to 2014-05-06.
